LABELS
------------
Why we have to use labels?

it is one of the identification thing for your pods
use these label you filter your pods
if you want to delete group of pods of you mention label automatically based on label it 
will delete every thin
how to create?
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: mypod
  labels:
    app: frontend
spec:
  containers:
    - name: mycont
      image: shaikmustafa/dm
      ports:
        - containerPort: 80
->kubectl get pods --show-labels--> it will show every label
->kubectl get pod -l app=frontend -> to see specific labels pod
->kubectl label pod <podname> env=project-> to attach label after creation
->kubectl label pod <podname> env - -> if you want to remove label
->kubectl label node <node name> node=worker1
