AUTO SCALING
------------
two type:
Horizantal scaleing-> it will increse no of servers if server limit is reached
Vertical scaling> it will server capacity if limit is reached

apiVersion: autoscaling/v2
kind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler
metadata:
  name: autoscale
spec:
  scaleTargetRef:
    apiVersion: apps/v1
    kind: Deployment
    name: mydeploy
  minReplicas: 2
  maxReplicas: 5

  metrics:
    - type: Resource
      resource:
        name: cpu
        target:
          type: Utilization
          averageUtilization: 50
->kubectl get hpa hpaname
->kubectl describe hpa hpaname
